  • Constructor Details

    • Guest

      public Guest(String name, String address, String country, String gender, String nationality, int contact, IDType idType, String identity, boolean isPayingGuest, PaymentType paymentType, CreditCard creditCard)
      Creates a guest object for a given name, address, country, gender, nationality, contact, ID type, identity, isPayingGuest, paymentType and Credit Card.
      Parameters:
      name - Name of this guest.
      address - Address of this guest.
      country - Country of this guest.
      gender - Gender of this guest (need not be male or female)
      nationality - Nationality of this guest.
      contact - Contact number of this guest.
      idType - ID type of guest (passport or driving license).
      identity - Last four characters of this guest's ID.
      isPayingGuest - If this guest is a paying guest or not.
      paymentType - Enumeration of Cash or Credit Card.
      creditCard - Credit Card of this guest.
